        <script>
            var isNameMetas = document.querySelector("meta[name ='nameContent']");
            if(isNameMetas != null)
            {
                var nameMetas = document.querySelector("meta[name ='nameContent']").getAttribute("content");
                if(nameMetas.charAt(nameMetas.length-1) == ']')
                    {
                        nameMetas = nameMetas.slice(0, -1);
                    } 

                    var splitData = nameMetas.split("];[");                    

                        splitData.forEach(function(entry) {
                                if( entry.charAt(0) == '[')
                                {
                                    entry = entry.slice(1);
                                }                                                           

                                var eachPair = entry.match(/([^,]*),(.*)/); 
                                if(eachPair != null)
                                {
                                    var m = document.createElement('meta'); 
                                    m.setAttribute('name', eachPair[1]);
                                    m.setAttribute('content', eachPair[2]);
                                    document.head.appendChild(m);
                                }
                            });  

                document.querySelector("meta[name ='nameContent']").remove();  
            }   
            
            var isPropMetas = document.querySelector("meta[name ='propertyContent']");
            if(isPropMetas != null)
            {
            var propMetas = document.querySelector("meta[name ='propertyContent']").getAttribute("content");
            if(propMetas.charAt(propMetas.length-1) == ']')
                {
                    propMetas = propMetas.slice(0, -1);
                } 

                var splitData = propMetas.split("];[");

                       splitData.forEach(function(entry) {
                            if( entry.charAt(0) == '[')
                                {
                                    entry = entry.slice(1);
                                }

                                
                            var eachPair = entry.match(/([^,]*),(.*)/); 
                            if(eachPair != null)
                            {
                                var m = document.createElement('meta'); 
                                m.setAttribute('property', eachPair[1]);
                                m.setAttribute('content', eachPair[2]);
                                document.head.appendChild(m);
                            }
                        });  

            document.querySelector("meta[name ='propertyContent']").remove();
            }
        </script>

        <script>

<div class="content-stripe-content"><h2>Nutrition</h2> <div class="rtf"><p>Providing you with healthy options is something your dining team proudly does every day. We help you select delicious, nutritious and satisfying meals, snacks and desserts by highlighting well-balanced menu choices and providing nutritional information and tips to help you make choices that fit your needs.</p></div> <a href="/explore/nutrition" target="_self" class="theme-button solid-button content-stripe-cta">Learn More</a></div> <div class="clear"></div></div></div><div><div class="content-stripe cs-image-right"><a href="#" target="_blank" class="cs-image"><img src="//content-service.sodexomyway.com/media/salad-for-homepage-nav-card_tcm390-74985.jpg?url=https://dining.muhlenberg.edu/" alt="salad"></a> <div class="content-stripe-content"><h2>Message Us</h2> <div class="rtf"><form action="/feedback" method="post"><label for="name" class="form-label"><span class="req">*</span> Name:</label><input name="name" type="text" id="name" title="name" required="required"><label for="Phone" class="form-label">Phone:</label><input name="Phone" type="phone" id="Phone" title="phone"><label for="email" class="form-label"><span class="req">*</span> Email:</label><input name="email" type="email" id="email" title="email" required="required"><label for="Customer Type" class="form-label"><label class="form-label">Message</label><textarea name="Message" id="Message" title="Message" required="required"></textarea></label><div id="inline-badge" class="captcha-box">&#xA0;</div><input type="hidden" id="captcha-response" name="captcha-response"><input class="theme-button solid-button form-button" type="submit" value="Submit"><input type="hidden" name="formtype" id="formtype" value="feedback"></form><script type="text/javascript">

        <script>
		$(document).ready(function(){
            if($("#page_main_content").length)
            {
			var $main = $("#page_main_content");
			var wonHeight = $(".sub_nav_inner_inner").height();			
			$main.css("min-height",wonHeight);
            }

            if($(".wiki-side-nav").length)
            {
			var $sideNav = $(".wiki-side-nav");
			var mainContent = $(".main-content").height();			
			$sideNav.css("max-height",mainContent);
            }
		});
	    </script>
        <!-- End: Global JavaScript Bottom -->
        

        <script>
            (function(){
                var cookieName = 'CurrentDomain';
                var cookieValue = 'https://dining.muhlenberg.edu/';
                var myDate = new Date();
                myDate.setMonth(myDate.getMonth() + 12);
                document.cookie = cookieName +"=" + cookieValue + ";expires=" + myDate 
                                + ";domain=.sodexomyway.com;path=/";
            })();

            
            (function(){
            var currentSite = 'Muhlenberg';
            if(currentSite.indexOf("Muhlenberg") > -1 || currentSite.indexOf("CustomMuhlenberg") > -1) 
            {
                var bodyEle = document.getElementsByTagName("body")[0]; 
                var homeClass = 'home beta-home fs-grid';
                if(homeClass && homeClass !=null)
                {
                    bodyEle.setAttribute('class', homeClass); 
                }
                else{
                bodyEle.setAttribute('class', 'fs-grid page_layout_default page_theme_header_slim');       
                } 
            }
            else
            {
                var className = 'home beta-home fs-grid';
                var bodyEle = document.getElementsByTagName("body")[0]; 
                bodyEle.setAttribute('class', className);  
            }

            if($(".tagembed-container").length)
            {
                var s = document.createElement("script");
                s.type = "text/javascript";
                s.src = "//widget.tagembed.com/embed.min.js";    
                $(".tagembed-container").append(s);

            }

            
            })();

        </script>
